definition: classics/sacred book/scripture/to pass through/to undergo/to bear/to endure/warp (textile)/longitude/menstruation/channel (TCM)/abbr. for economics 經濟|经济[jing1 ji4]
to cross/to go over/to pass (time)/to celebrate (a holiday)/to live/to get along/excessively/too-

sentences.english: The result is, that it is not necessary to use gibberlin acid.
sentences.chinese: 实验结果是，种子不必经过酸处理也可以发芽。

sentences.english: Made of specially-treated material, the coat is light in weight and machine washable.
sentences.chinese: 该大衣由经过特殊处理的面料做成，重量轻，可机洗。

sentences.english: Air whips past the blades of a turbine, forcing it to spin.
sentences.chinese: 经过风轮叶片的空气迫使风轮旋转，风轮驱动电机。

sentences.english: Judging by recent form, he should easily pass the exam.
sentences.chinese: 全队经过六个月的训练竞技状态极佳。

sentences.english: Through many dangers, toils, and snares I have already come.
sentences.chinese: 许多危险，试练网罗，我已安然经过。

sentences.english: The subject of this study was the defatted fly maggot.
sentences.chinese: 本研究以经过脱脂处理的蝇蛆为试验材料。

sentences.english: Walking home by the alma mater is just for seeking fun.
sentences.chinese: 经过母校步行回家仅仅为了取乐而已。

sentences.english: At the mean time, the vulture went by. The potion was polluted by the unexpectedly fallen hair.
sentences.chinese: 同时，秃鹰正巧经过，秃鹰的头发无意间落入魔药内。

sentences.english: Adenoviruses have been modified to carry parts of the HIV virus.
sentences.chinese: 腺病毒经过改良以携带HIV病毒部件。

sentences.english: Happened, the vessel motorboat to save not escape.
sentences.chinese: 刚巧，有艘汽艇经过，拯救尚未逃生者。

sentences.english: To narrate is to give an account of what happened or is happening.
sentences.chinese: 记叙文讲述的是发生在当前或过去事情的经过。

sentences.english: II. 199 foreign business invested commercial enterprises need to make rectifications after sorting out.
sentences.chinese: 经过清理需要进行整改的外商投资商业企业199家。

sentences.english: And finally let's pass by the Waterbird Refuge.
sentences.chinese: 最后，我们经过了水鸟保护区。

sentences.english: Lancers and dancers pass a poisoned syringe.
sentences.chinese: 枪骑兵和舞者经过一次被投毒的注射。

sentences.english: Experiments show the proper application of this method can improve the effects of shot-put teaching.
sentences.chinese: 经过实验研究，合理运用可以优化教学效果。

sentences.english: I succeeded in passing the driving test.
sentences.chinese: 我乐成地经过了驾驶测验。
